08:13.785 --> 08:16.242
on how you got that 9-millimeter bullet
in your head.

08:16.287 --> 08:18.278
(sighs)

08:20.667 --> 08:23.625
(police radio chatter,
sea gull squawking)

08:24.462 --> 08:26.077
(Chris) Uh, is there anyone
you'd like us to call?

08:26.131 --> 08:29.294
Huh? No. Uh, no.
I, uh, I live alone.

08:30.427 --> 08:33.169
Um, any family?
A-Anyone you work with?

08:33.221 --> 08:36.008
Work with? At my age?

08:36.057 --> 08:37.672
I'm actually flattered.

08:37.726 --> 08:39.842
Well, the EMS will finish
checking you out.

08:39.894 --> 08:43.136
You're a very nice young man,
very courteous.

08:43.189 --> 08:45.145
You're a--You're a good boy.

08:45.191 --> 08:46.647
(Jerry) Diaz.

08:46.693 --> 08:48.308
Yeah. Excuse me.

08:48.361 --> 08:50.317
Oh, of course.
Yes. Yes, I'm sorry.

08:50.363 --> 08:51.352
He tell you what happened?

08:51.406 --> 08:53.317
Uh, cyclist swerved in front of him,
car had a mind of its own.

08:54.075 --> 08:55.281
You know... (scoffs)

08:55.326 --> 08:58.284
should be mandatory retesting
for every driver over 50.

08:58.705 --> 09:01.913
