Poor old guy.

09:01.958 --> 09:04.290
Goes out for a drive,
ends up killing someone. It's awful.

09:04.335 --> 09:06.747
Yeah? A little bit worse
for the cyclist, wouldn't you say?

09:08.214 --> 09:09.920
Okay, I'm gonna wait for the coroner.

09:09.966 --> 09:12.252
You and Gail make sure the old guy's car
gets to impound.

09:12.844 --> 09:13.833
All right?

09:13.887 --> 09:16.219
- Uh, yes, sir.
- Okay.

09:16.264 --> 09:19.222
Man, what the hell
have you been smokin'?

09:19.267 --> 09:21.633
How could I be walking around
with a bullet in my head?

09:21.686 --> 09:23.142
