09:34.407 --> 09:38.320
Well, then this constitutes...
unlawful... containment!

09:38.369 --> 09:39.745
Unlawful confinement.

09:40.622 --> 09:41.907
Which is not applicable here.

09:41.956 --> 09:44.823
Uh, this is more, uh,
investigative detention.

09:46.544 --> 09:47.920
We are taking him
to the hospital, right?

09:47.962 --> 09:50.123
Oh, yeah. And we're gonna get
an X-ray of that bullet.

09:50.173 --> 09:51.879
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
No, no, no, no. Hey, hey.

09:51.925 --> 09:53.415
I don't do hospitals, okay?

09:53.468 --> 09:55.254
Look, they're gonna give me
a needle or something.

09:55.303 --> 09:57.009
I don't want anything to do with that.

09:57.055 --> 09:58.545
You should've thought of that
before you got hooked up

09:58.598 --> 10:00.384
with a bunch of carjackers,
jackbrain.

10:03.895 --> 10:06.136
(Benny) I don't like X-rays.
They freak me out.

10:06.189 --> 10:08.396
(Andy) Okay, well, then try
to get your mind off of it.

10:08.441 --> 10:11.729
Maybe tell me what happened
when the guy got shot at the parking garage.

10:12.654 --> 10:14.360
I don't remember any parking garage.

10:14.405 --> 10:16.111
I got a bullet in my head, remember?

10:17.742 --> 10:20.734
You know, you dress pretty nice
for a guy who doesn't have a job.

10:21.913 --> 10:25.030
Who says I don't have a job?
| freelance.

10:25.083 --> 10:27.870
(laughs) Is that so?

10:27.919 --> 10:29.375
(chuckles) Yeah.

10:29.420 --> 10:32.378
